<bibRefCitation id="D0F405D2A924681A88ACDB2C8CFCB22D" DOI="https://doi.org/10.2307/4114408" author="Blakelock, RA" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="177 - 224" refId="B4" refString="Blakelock, RA, 1957. Notes on the Flora of Iraq with keys - Part III. Caryophyllaceae (including Illecebraceae). Kew Bulletin 2 (2): 177 - 224, DOI: https://doi.org/10.2307/4114408" title="Notes on the Flora of Iraq with keys - Part III. Caryophyllaceae (including Illecebraceae)." url="https://doi.org/10.2307/4114408" volume="2" year="1957">Blakelock (1957)</bibRefCitation>
