<normalizedToken id="51EB02AF8500A0BC9BAB246FE9B3D139" originalValue="Decaisne’s">Decaisne's</normalizedToken>
description was published. The name 
<taxonomicName id="55349740DC8A8305BFD45A329628755C" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Silene" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Silene linearis" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="linearis">
<emphasis id="4ACE2B88FDA9E536958E30AD002C6C9C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Silene linearis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Sweet has been cited by few authors. 
<bibRefCitation id="189BA2A5520FA5B3D5ADD30A00BCA11A" DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.15462" author="Rohrbach, P" journalOrPublisher="Systematic Botany" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B54" refString="Rohrbach, P, 1868. Monographie der Gattung Silene. W. Engelmann, Leipzig, 1-249. https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.15462" title="Monographie der Gattung Silene. W. Engelmann, Leipzig, 1 - 249." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.15462" year="1868">Rohrbach (1868)</bibRefCitation>
